11:07.567 --> 11:09.000
to file an appeal
on your behalf.

11:09.066 --> 11:10.600
- Beecher, please don't.

11:10.667 --> 11:12.333
- It's something I have to do.

11:12.400 --> 11:15.300
We gotta get a hold
of that tape.

11:15.367 --> 11:18.333
It's got the fight
between Keane and the Latinos.

11:18.400 --> 11:21.000
