in the murder.

11:24.100 --> 11:27.367
Well, do what you can, Bob.

11:27.433 --> 11:29.100
- Sure.

11:29.166 --> 11:32.934
- There you are.

11:33.000 --> 11:35.533
- Oh, yeah, hey.

11:35.600 --> 11:37.467
- Why did you go into "P.C."?

11:37.533 --> 11:40.834
- You know, I just needed
some time alone.

11:42.500 --> 11:43.633
- What are you doing here?

11:43.700 --> 11:45.600
- Working on
Ryan O'Reily's appeal.

11:45.667 --> 11:47.400
- Really?

11:47.467 --> 11:48.867
Thought you said
that was useless.

11:48.934 --> 11:50.734
- Well...

11:50.800 --> 11:53.133
